{"tid":1560433,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[一句講哂] 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-09-11T07:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T01:11:04.000Z","uid":2634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8b5a042b0d41ea4eca52258de5d5198c141568","tid":1560433,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:50:10.000Z","msg":"依個Post好簡單 8隻字就可以講完<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求，<span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可。</span></span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n為左方便大家記得咩叫「五大訴求」，我會詳細列出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 成立獨立委員會<br />\n3. 撤回所有暴動定性<br />\n4. 永不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n5. 全面落實真「雙普選」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請謹記，係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你可以笑我地係痴人說夢，你可以盡情咁笑，但當五大訴求逐一實現，你就知我地係咩料！<br />\n<img src=\"https://001.img.pu.sohu.com.cn/group1/M04/A5/67/MTAuMTguMTcuMTg2/MTAwMTM1XzE1NTU1NjA4MjM0OTQ=.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F001.img.pu.sohu.com.cn%2Fgroup1%2FM04%2FA5%2F67%2FMTAuMTguMTcuMTg2%2FMTAwMTM1XzE1NTU1NjA4MjM0OTQ%3D.jpg&h=b06a93af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講完，多謝大家！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFzz0Ww.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFzz0Ww.gif&h=390cd6f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"510f175621a968f4fe6d90fe25599a7fce24bca6","tid":1560433,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4599a1520e2b6bc7e88740d6f7a2d08bfea8900","tid":1560433,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe8b8c5322dbe078023774a42f6adac2ab26f80d","tid":1560433,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:55:27.000